  </ThingDef>
  
  <ThingDef ParentName="CavePlantBase">
    <defName>Plant_AOSGitz_LoonCap</defName>
    <label>Looncap</label>
    <description>Powerful fungi of varying sizes found only in places touched by Da Bad Moons light, they are highly coveted by the Gloomspite Gitz for all manner of rituals and potions. It can grow on fungal gravel, but only in darkness - exposing it to any kind of light, including darklights, will kill it.</description>
